  "page": "Dagger Lake",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dagger Lake is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Dagger Lake is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 58.3%; left: 68.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Dagger Lake\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Dagger Lake</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of Dagger Lake\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG/350px-Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG\" width=\"350\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG/525px-Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG 1.5x, /images/6/6d/Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aurelien_Hubert_Dagger_Lake_Galley.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A galley in Dagger Lake © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dagger_Lake.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/Dagger_Lake.jpg/350px-Dagger_Lake.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/Dagger_Lake.jpg/525px-Dagger_Lake.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/Dagger_Lake.jpg/700px-Dagger_Lake.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dagger_Lake.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>© Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Dagger Lake</b> is a large lake formed by the confluence of the rivers <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Qhoyne\" title=\"Qhoyne\">Qhoyne</a> in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> At Dagger Lake the Qhoyne comes rushing in, full of gold and amber from the <a href=\"/index.php/Axe\" title=\"Axe\">Axe</a> and pine-cones from the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Northeast of Dagger Lake are the ruins of <a href=\"/index.php/Ar_Noy\" title=\"Ar Noy\">Ar Noy</a>, while along its western banks are the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Fields\" title=\"Golden Fields\">Golden Fields</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Dagger Lake is full of islands where <a href=\"/index.php/Pirates\" title=\"Pirates\">pirates</a> lurk in hidden caves and secret strongholds, such as <a href=\"/index.php/Urho\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Urho\">Urho the Unwashed</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Korra\" title=\"Korra\">Korra the Cruel</a> on <i><a href=\"/index.php/Hag%27s_Teeth\" title=\"Hag&#39;s Teeth\">Hag's Teeth</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagger_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/War_on_Dagger_Lake\" title=\"War on Dagger Lake\">War on Dagger Lake</a> was one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynish_Wars\" title=\"Rhoynish Wars\">Rhoynish Wars</a> between the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvos</a> broke <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> power on the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> in a battle involving fire galleys on Dagger Lake.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagger_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagger_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Motho\" title=\"Motho\">Motho</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> have been reported north of Dagger Lake.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> passes Dagger Lake by night, unseen and unmolested by pirates.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagger_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 14\">Chapter 14</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_not